title: Aphex Twin user18081971 (tracks 001-230) [soundcloud]
description:
On January 25, 2015, Richard D. James (Aphex Twin, AFX) began uploading over 230 previously unreleased tracks to SoundCloud, first as /user48736353001 and later as /user18081971.

The majority of tracks were made available for download as 320 kbps MP3s.

This torrent contains all 230 tracks uploaded through May 22, 2015.

ID3v2.3 tags include track names as they appear in RDJ's original files and comments featuring track info and #hashtags written by RDJ.

The tracklist is sequenced to match the order in which RDJ uploaded the tracks.


I care because you do. PLEASE SEED
